gle: URL Dedup at Scale","target":"Notion Knowledge/Note/How to avoid crawling duplicate URLs at Google scale","line":79},{"title":"Uber Eats: Image Dedup","target":"Notion Knowledge/Note/How Uber Eats Deduplicates Hundreds of Millions of Product Images","line":81},{"title":"Why SSDs Are Fast","target":"Notion Knowledge/Note/Why is a solid-state drive (SSD) fast","line":83},{"title":"Why Executives Seem Out of Touch","target":"Notion Knowledge/Note/Why Executives Seem Out of Touch, and How to Reach Them","line":85},{"title":"MOC-Distributed-Systems","target":"MOC-Distributed-Systems","line":92},{"title":"MOC-Database","target":"MOC-Database","line":93},{"title":"MOC-Java","target":"MOC-Java","line":94},{"title":"MOC-PDMS","target":"MOC-PDMS","line":95},{"title":"🏗️ Hub — Tổng index","target":"Microservices-Patterns/00-Hub-Microservices-Patterns","line":102},{"title":"⚡ Cheat Sheet — Quick Reference","target":"Microservices-Patterns/Cheat-Sheet","line":103},{"title":"📦 Data & Consistency","target":"Microservices-Patterns/01-Data-Consistency","line":104},{"title":"📡 Communication","target":"Microservices-Patterns/02-Communication","line":105},{"title":"🛡️ Reliability","target":"Microservices-Patterns/03-Reliability","line":106},{"title":"🔭 Observability","target":"Microservices-Patterns/04-Observability","line":107},{"title":"✂️ Decomposition & Deployment","target":"Microservices-Patterns/05-Decomposition","line":108}],"metadata":{"tags":["#moc","#architecture","#design-patterns","#clean-architecture","#ddd"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"_moc/MOC-System-Design.md"},
